(87, 1, 'Shiseido IBUKI Refining Moisturizer (75ml)', '&lt;div class=&quot;content&quot; style=&quot;word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 20px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;Shiseido IBUKI Refining Moisturizer is an emulsion with an ultra-light touch and a dewy, moist feeling. Formulated with PhytoResist Complex which boosts skin’s strength to resist problems. This multi-action formula intensively corrects the appearance of unevenness such as visible pores, breakouts/blemish marks and skin roughness by building skin’s strength to resist problems. Renews the skin’s surface to reveal an incredibly smooth, uniform texture. The appearance of fine lines caused by dryness is reduced, keeping skin hydrated all day long.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', '', 'Shiseido IBUKI Refining Moisturizer (75ml)', '', '');
