(95, 1, 'L\'Oreal Paris DERMO-EXPERTISE REVITALIFT Milky Foam (100ml)', '&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Gently cleanses the skin every day:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;new Revitalift Milky Foam instantly removes make-up, cleanses skin thoroughly and eliminates all impurities for an impeccably clean skin.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Prepares the skin to complete anti-wrinkle + firming routine: fighting against signs of aging starts with a perfectly cleansed skin, well-conditioned to receive the benefits of active&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'L\'Oreal Paris DERMO-EXPERTISE REVITALIFT Milky Foam (100ml)', '', ''),
