(98, 1, 'L\'Oreal Paris HYDRAFRESH Hydrating Refreshing Creamy Foam (125ml)', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;L\'Oreal Paris Hydrafresh Hydrating Refreshing Creamy Foam cleanses your skin with this gentle facial foam, combined with hydrating essence and essential minerals. Skin is left soft, hydrated and refreshed with no feeling of tightness.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'L\'Oreal Paris HYDRAFRESH Hydrating Refreshing Creamy Foam (125ml)', '', ''),
