(140, 1, 'L\'oreal - Professionnel Mythic Oil Shampoo with Argan Oil &amp; Myrrh (Thick Hair)', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;An oil-infused shampoo for thick, unruly hair&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: 0px; font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Inspired by the tradition of Indian oil bathing&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: 0px; font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Produces a generous foam to gently cleanse &amp;amp; tame hair&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: 0px; font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Contains fairly traded argan oil to deeply nourish hair&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: 0px; font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Blended with myrrh extract for healing &amp;amp; repairing properties&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: 0px; font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Leaves hair soft, smooth &amp;amp; shiny&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: 0px; font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Dermatologist-tested, paraben-free&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'L\'oreal - Professionnel Mythic Oil Shampoo with Argan Oil &amp; Myrrh (Thick Hair)', '', ''),
(137, 1, 'Sulwhasoo Basic Care Kit (5pcs) (5piece)', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Sulwhasoo Basic Care Kit (5pcs) contains:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;First Care Activating Serum EX (Miniature) (8ml)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;First Care Activating Serum EX is an essential regimen first-step serum formulated with JAUM Balancing Complex assures optimal skincare results by restoring balance to skin. Product Features: 	Help to balance your skin and boost the absorption and effectiveness of any treatments used after it. 	Create the optimum balance of moisture, transparency and suppleness. 	Rejuvenating the skin’s vitality, generate the glowing radiance of healthy skin.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Essential Balancing Water EX (Miniature) (15ml)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Essential Balancing Water EX is a gel-textured toner that prepares skin for deep moisturization. The properties of Matrimony Vine relax the skin, while Purslane provides hydration, leaving your skin with a delicate veil of moisture. Product Features:  Hydrating 	Soothing 	Nourishing 	Leaving the skin supple&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Essential Balancing Emulsion EX (Miniature) (15ml)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Essential Balancing Emulsion EX is a moisture-rich emulsion that absorbs quickly for soft and smooth skin. It is formulated with Mountain Peony extract that softens and refines skin texture, while Yai Jiu Hua helps improve skin clarity. Product Features: 	Hydrating 	Smoothing 	Nourishing 	Leaving the skin supple&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Essential Rejuvenating Eye Cream (Miniature) (3.5ml)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Nano-particles care eyes skin and significantly soft the skin around eyes. The unique formulation technology of nano-particles like Essence to your eye skin gives light and comfortable feel. Enzymes from Korean Red Ginseng Saponin effectively diminish the appearance of fine lines around the eyes, while Yai Jiu Hua and honey rejuvenate the skin to keep it healthy. Product Features: 	Revitalize the delicate skin around the eyes by enhancing blood circulation of eye. 	Improve skin wrinkles, dark eye circle and bags under eye. 	Smoothly wraps the skin in moisture, leaving a silky finish.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Concentrated Ginseng Renewing Cream (Miniature) (5ml)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Concentrated Ginseng Renewing Cream is formulated with the essence of a whole ginseng, it can be penetrated to the deepest layers of the skin to revive damaged, youth-depleted skin from within. Multiple Features: 	Ginseng crystals, which have been extracted from the root and fruit, fortify the skin\'s delicate inner layers and defend against signs of aging while boosting the skin\'s own defensive barrier. 	By applying Sulwhasoo’s own Ginsenomics™, this advanced bioconversion technology to deliver ginseng’s anti-aging properties directly into your skin. 	Skin becomes supple, moisturized and revitalized with ginseng’s rejuvenating powers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Sulwhasoo Basic Care Kit (5pcs) (5piece)', '', '');
