(266, 1, 'Estee Lauder RADIANT HEALTH Day and Night Radiance Set (2piece)', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Estée Lauder Radiant Health Day and Night Radiance Set contains:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;“Estée Lauder Nutritious Vitality 8™ Radiant Moisture Crème” (50ml)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Recharge and renew your skin for a energized look every day. Designated for Asian young women, the Radiant Moisture Crème instantly refreshes skin’s radiance with light hydration and nutrients. This innovative dual-phase formula enhances skin’s internal moisture barrier, leaving skin look fresh and imbued with radiant vitality. This all-day moisturizer not only keeps your skin refreshed, but instantly hydrates your skin with brightening effect to help combat dullness.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Enriched with exclusive Pomegranate Complex, the cream activates eight key dimensions of healthy-looking skin, including smoothness, refinement, supplement, calmness, energy, radiance, hydration and nourishment. Luscious crème formula delivers instant hydration that strengthens skin’s moisture barrier. Nutritious including cucumber extract and berry extract neutralize external irritants and detoxify toxins. As an effective approach to beautify your skin, this all-day moisturizer helps you see a new look of radiant, active skin with daily dose of powerful vita-nutrients.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Multiple effects:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;	Dual detoxification: infused with exclusive pomegranate complex, the formula provides anti-oxidant power that radicals and toxins. Skin feels refreshed and hydrated.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;	Sign treatment: improves skin’s elasticity, soothes fine lines, and prevents the formation of wrinkles&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;	Whitening effect: restores skin’s hydration and skin texture, boosts metabolism, skin remains nourished and calmed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;“Estée Lauder Nutritious Vitality 8™ Night Radiant Overnight Crème/Mask” (50ml)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Power up and recharge your skin with this night radiant overnight crème. Providing multiple benefits including nourishing and recharging skin’s radiance, this rich overnight moisture crème provides deep hydration and reactivates skin’s natural moisture defenses. Contained strong anti-irritant properties, the crème has the effect of calming and soothing Asian skin, helping it recover from visible effects of environmental damage.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Featuring hydrating function, this night radiant overnight crème/mask supports skin’s nstural moisture balance. Enriched with Estée Lauder’s exclusive Pomegranate8™ Complex coupled with vitamins and minerals that are essential to bright-looking skin, the formula restores skin’s balance and infuses deep nourishment. It can also be used as a nightly mask for overnight nutrient infusion. Within two-week time, skin reveals to be more smooth, radiant, refined, supple, calmed and energized.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &am