(307, 1, 'OLAY - Daily Renewal Cleanser', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;A skin renewing facial foam wash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: 0px; font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Contains gentle massaging micro-beads to lift away impurities &amp;amp; dull surface cells&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: 0px; font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Blended with BHA to promote skin turnover&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: 0px; font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Reduces the appearance of fine lines&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;outline: 0px; font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-se