(308, 1, 'Estee Lauder RESILIENCE LIFT NIGHT Firming/Sculpting Face and Neck Creme (50ml)', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Estée Lauder RESILIENCE LIFT NIGHT Firming/Sculpting Face and Neck Creme contains exclusive Nocturnal Lift Complex to help give skin the critical time it needs to boost its natural production of collagen and support proteins for a more intensive nighttime lift. Your skin will look younger, more lifted, firmer and newly defined the next morning. It also brings a fresh, rejuvenated glow.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Estee Lauder RESILIENCE LIFT NIGHT Firming/Sculpting Face and Neck Creme (50ml)', '', ''),
(309, 1, 'Estee Lauder - Enlighten Dark Spot Correcting Night Serum', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;An intensive brightening night serum Features an ultra-lightweight, quick-dissolving texture Formulated with biomimetic enzyme &amp;amp; plum blossom extract Helps reduce the look of dark spots, discolorations, blotchiness &amp;amp; redness Contains sodium hyaluronate plus sunflower, barley &amp;amp; cucumber extracts&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Estee Lauder - Enlighten Dark Spot Correcting Night Serum', '', ''),
