(78, 2, 'OLAY - Natural White UV Natural Lightening Cream SPF 18', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;A whitening &amp;amp; protecting day cream Developed with multi Vitamin WTN technology containing vitamins B3, B5 &amp;amp; E Helps inhibit melanin formation &amp;amp; corrects skin tone Delivers long-lasting hydration for up to 24 hours Shields skin against broad spectrum UV rays with SPF 18/PA++&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'OLAY - Natural White UV Natural Lightening Cream SPF 18', '', '');
