(81, 2, 'L\'Oreal Paris EXCELLENCE CREME Excellence Cream (1 Natural Black) (1box)', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Protective Pre-color Serum 12ml&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Protective Crème Colorant 48ml&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Crème Developer 72ml&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Protective Conditioner 40ml&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Excellence Crème is a hair color which protects your hair due to its triple care formula: an advanced technology concentrating 3 powerful ingredients that strengthens your hair while coloring, leaving it softer and protected.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Hair feels soft and silky. Color looks sensational with perfect grey coverage.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'L\'Oreal Paris EXCELLENCE CREME Excellence Cream (1 Natural Black) (1box)', '', ''),
(82, 2, 'Shiseido BENEFIANCE NutripPerfect Eye Serum (15ml)', '&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Shiseido Benefiance NutriPerfect Eye Serum is a total eye treatment created especially for mature skin experiencing all visible signs associated with hormonal changes due to aging. As skin’s fundamental structure weakens, wrinkles and skin sagginess become apparent.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Formulated with concentrated Carnosine DPTM, and multivitamins B,C,E, a powerful nutritive supplement, this serum effectively improves loss of firmness and wrinkles for an impeccably youthful appearance.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Its light silky texture allows quick absorption and immediately replenishes rich moisture to achieve beautifully smooth and soft skin around the eye area. It also reduces appearance of dark circles and dullness while boosting radiance around the eye area.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;In a week, sagging and fine lines will be visibly reduced. The look of crow’s feet will dramatically improves in three weeks time.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Shiseido BENEFIANCE NutripPerfect Eye Serum (15ml)', '', ''),
(138, 2, 'Estee Lauder ADVANCED NIGHT REPAIR Advanced Night Repair Face Serum &amp; Eye Gel Creme Set (2piece)', '', '', 'Estee Lauder ADVANCED NIGHT REPAIR Advanced Night Repair Face Serum &amp; Eye Gel Creme Set (2piece)', '', ''),
(84, 2, 'L\'Oreal Paris MAGIC RETOUCH (75ml) (DARK BROWN)', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;The 1st ROOT CONCEALER SPRAY TOTALLY COVERS ROOTS IN 3 SECONDS&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'L\'Oreal Paris MAGIC RETOUCH (75ml) (DARK BROWN)', '', ''),
(171, 2, 'Estee Lauder - Advanced Night Repair Synchronized Recovery Complex II', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;An ultimate, advanced anti-aging serum Inspired by groundbreaking DNA research to help reduction of visible signs of aging Provides intense moisture to keep skin hydrated Neutralizes harmful effect of free radicals, external factors &amp;amp; emotional stress Repairs past damage, prevents future damage Leaves skin smooth, supple &amp;amp; youthful&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Estee Lauder - Advanced Night Repair Synchronized Recovery Complex II', '', ''),
