uot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;Leaves skin white, radiant &amp;amp; even-toned&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'OLAY - Milky Fair Cleanser', '', ''),
(311, 2, 'Giorgio Armani - Designer Lift Smoothing Firming Foundation SPF20 - # 4', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: proxima_nova, Arial, &amp;quot;Heiti TC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft JhengHei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, PMingLiU, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;&quot;&gt;A groundbreaking, protective fluid foundation Boasts Stretching Micro-fil TM technology that wraps face with an ultra-fine micro-lifting matrix Retains a high concentration of exclusive emollients &amp;amp; velvet filters Instantly stretches, softens &amp;amp; firms skin\'s surface Protects skin against harmful UV rays with SPF 20&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'Giorgio Armani - Designer Lift Smoothing Firming Foundation SPF20 - # 4', '', ''),
(312, 2, 'Estee Lauder RESILIENCE LIFT Firming/Sculpting Face and Neck Creme SPF 15(Dry Skin) (50ml)', '&lt;div class=&quot;content&quot; style=&quot;word-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 20px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;Estee Lauder Resilience Lift&lt;br&gt;Firming/Sculpting Face and Neck Creme SPF 15 will give you a all-the lifted look, the firmer feeling and the radiance that reflects how beautiful you are. Powered by our exclusive Photo-Activated Lift Complex, Resilience Lift day formulas harness the beneficial power of visible light. Featuring a light-responsive enzyme (Plankton Extract), mineral (Malachite) and plant extract (Mimosa) to help skin amplify its natural collagen and elastin production.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Over time, skin\'s strength, resiliency and volume are renewed and you\'ll see a remarkably younger, revitalized look.&lt;br&gt;•	Immediately, skin looks more radiantly alive and fresher-younger.&lt;br&gt;•	As you use it, facial contours appear sculpted and newly defined.&lt;br&gt;•	Lines and wrinkles look more smoothed out and lifted away.&lt;br&gt;•	An advanced blend of lipids and more infuse skin with rich, lasting moisture.&lt;br&gt;•	Use it with Resilience Lift Night for a multi-faceted, 24-Hour lift.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;In clinical testing, 92% of women showed a significantly more lifted look in just 4 weeks.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', '', 'Estee Lauder RESILIENCE LIFT Firming/Sculpting Face and Neck Creme SPF 15(Dry Skin) (50ml)', '', ''),
(313, 2, 'Estee Lauder RADIANT HEALTH Nutritious Vitality8™ Night Radiant Overnight Creme/Mask (50ml)', '&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;“Estée Lauder Nutritious Vitality8™ Night Radiant Overnight Creme/Mask” (50ml)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Power up and recharge your skin with this night radiant overnight crème. Providing multiple benefits including nourishing and recharging skin’s radiance, this rich overnight moisture crème provides deep hydration and reactivates skin’s natural moisture defenses. Contained strong anti-irritant properties, the crème has the effect of calming and soothing Asian skin, helping it recover from visible effects of environmental damage.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Featuring hydrating function, this night radiant overnight crème/mask supports skin’s nstural moisture balance. Enriched with Estée Lauder’s exclusive Pomegranate8™ Complex coupled with vitamins and minerals that are essential to bright-looking skin, the formula restores skin’s balance and infuses deep nourishment. It can also be used as a nightly mask for overnight nutrient infusion. Within two-week time, skin reveals to be more smooth, radiant, refined, supple, calmed and energized.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Multiple effects:&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Reactivates skin’s natural moisture defenses: overnight, the mask replenishes skin’s hydration for a radiant vitality.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Intensive infusion of vitamins: exclusive Pomegranate8™ Complex supports skin’s natural healthy looking balance, creating the optimal condition for skin to perform at its peak.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style=&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &amp;quot;Microsoft Yahei&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, &amp;quot; Helvetica&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Enhances anti-oxidant power: protects skin from radical damage, amplifies skin’s natural ability to neutralize environmental aggressors with lasting antioxidant power. The pink peony extract helps bloom your skin with new nourishment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;', '', 'Estee Lauder RADIANT HEALTH Nutritious Vitality8™ Night Radiant Overnight Creme/Mask (50ml)', '', ''),
